# 🥗 7. Smart Diet Planner ("શું જમવું?")

One of the best additions.

Based on diagnosis, the system recommends suitable foods.

Example:

## Diabetes

Eat:

- Salad
- Whole wheat roti
- Green vegetables

Avoid:

- Sweets
- Soft drinks
- White rice

---

## Dengue

Eat:

- Coconut water
- Kiwi
- Pomegranate
- Papaya
- Soup

Drink:

- 4–5 litres of fluids (as advised by the doctor)

---

## Kidney Disease

Avoid:

- High salt
- High potassium foods

Recommended:

- Doctor-approved renal diet

---

## Pregnancy

Recommend:

- Iron-rich foods
- Calcium-rich foods
- Protein-rich meals

